seo.title: Praiano: spokojny sąsiad Positano
seo.description: Urok Praiano: plaże, szlaki, dojazd i komu najbardziej przypadnie do gustu.

sections.title: Why visit
body: Enjoy panoramic sunsets from Piazza San Gennaro without elbow-to-elbow crowds.

sections.title: Beaches & swimming
body: Gavitella Beach faces west for golden-hour swims; count 400 steps down, so plan snacks and water.

sections.title: Food & nightlife
body: Praiano's beach bars host live music on weekends—check posters near the SITA stop for set times.
